pageContext.claim: “James Comey’s Memos are Classified, I did not Declassify them. They belong to our Government! Therefore, he broke the law! Additionally, he totally made up many of the things he said I said, and he is already a proven liar and leaker. Where are Memos on Clinton, Lynch & others?”
pageContext.analysis: The only memo that Comey shared with the media, concerning Trump's request that Comey drop the Michael Flynn investigation, was not classified. He shared three other memos with an attorney, but is said to have redacted any secret or classified material.
